:: UnitActionChoose [nobr]

<<set $gMenuVisible = false>>

<<set _unit = $unit[$gUnitSelected_key]>>

What would you like to do for <<rep _unit>>?

<<unitactionlist setup.unitaction _unit>>


:: TrainingDo[nobr]

<<set _unit = $unit[$gUnitSelected_key]>>
<<set _unittraining = setup.unitaction[$gTrainingSelected_key]>>
<<unset $gTrainingSelected_key>>
<<unset $gUnitSelected_key>>

<<run _unittraining.generateQuest(_unit)>>

<<focgoto 'QuestHub'>>

